    <section id=dress>
      <div> 
        <h2><span></span><span>Dress Considerations</span><span></span></h2>
        <p>The wedding is formal, and we invite you to dress in style! Zoo-themed clothing welcomed! However, as this is an outdoor wedding, we do encourage guests to bring comfortable footwear for walking, and to bring extra clothing in case of rain.
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id=registry>
      <div>
        <h2><span></span><span>Registry</span><span></span></h2>
        <p>We are registered for wedding gifts at Home Outfitters, and Mountain Equipment Co-op. Registry gifts can be purchased in stores, or online. Follow the links below to view registry items under Jonathan and Janessa Suderman. Alternately, we are pleased to accept monetary gifts. 
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id=rsvp>
      <div>
        <h2><span></span><span>RSVP</span><span></span></h2>
        <p>Please indicate whether you plan to attend by no later than April 30, 2013.
        <br><br>
        <form action=rsvp method=post>
          <label class=response for=response>Will you be joining us?</label><br>
          <input type=radio name=response value="Yep!"> Of course&mdash;I wouldn't miss it!<br>
          <input type=radio name=response value="Nope!"> Sorry, I wish I could make it.
        </form>
      </div>
